episodes: Pyaar Na.. Thoda Complicated Hota Hai..!!
Pyaar Andha Hota Hai Suna Tha
Waqt Ne Kiya Kya Haseen Sitam Tum Rahe Na Tum, Hum Rahe Na Hum
Aap Se Tum Tak Ka Safar
Bin Bole Sab Jaanta Hai... Dil Ko Dil Se Baandhta Hai... Kitna Bholasa Ye Pyaar Hai
Ye Kya Ghadi Hai... Hum Ajnabi Hain... Duniya Meri Kyu Mujhse Khafa Hai
Chaahe Kitni Dooriyaan Hongi Darmiyaan... Sunn Raha Phir Bhi Dil, Dil Ki Ye Daastaan
Ye Ishq Ab Le Jo Imtehaan... Dene Chale Hum Beparwaah
Ghadi Waqt Dikhati Hai, Waqt Deti Nahi Hai
Lamhon Se Likhdi Ek Daastaan... Khamoshiyon Ki Padhtey Zubaan
Dheere Chalne Se Peeche Chhoot Jaate Hain... Tez Chalne Se Yaadein Peeche Chhoot Jaati Hain
Tujhse Hi Roothe Roothe.. Tujhme Hi Toote Toote
Kisi Ek Ki Wajah Se, Do Logon Ko Dukhi Nahi Hona Chahiye
Tumhari Wajah Bhi Badal Gayi Hai, Hamare Haalat Ki Tarah
Tumhi Uljhe Rahe Hamein Aazmane Mein
Mera Kuch Saaman, Tumhare Paas Padha Hai
Ab Bas, Aaramse Iss Divorce Ko Ho Jaane Do
Do Shaadiyaan Ek Saath Start Hui Aur Ek Saath Khatam Bhi
The End.. Prem Kahani Wo Badi Banti Hai Jismein Aanewali Mushkilein Badi Badi Hon
